summary: I follow a good number of blogs but a lot of them seem to be inactive. I want more people on my dash. If you post anything of...
body:
I follow a good number of blogs but a lot of them seem to be inactive. I want more people on my dash. If you post anything of the below like or reblog this post and I’ll check out your blog:

Avatar: The Last Airbender (I’m obviously a Zutara shipper but that’s not a requirement as long as you aren’t an aggressive hater. I want more general ATLA content.)

Killing Eve (Either ship Villaneve or don’t mind the fact that people ship Villaneve. Basically, no fun suckers lol)

Black Sails (I’d like more content about the wlw characters in particular. (Max, Eleanor, and Anne).

Shameless US (Honestly mainly just Mickey stans and Gallavich shippers. I don’t really care about the rest of the show anymore lmao)

Game of Thrones/A Song of Ice and Fire (Sansa and House Stark stans. No Sansa haters)

Life is Strange (Pricefield or Amberpricefield shippers please)

The Hunger Games (No Peeta or Everlark haters)

Follow backs are not necessary. I just wanna fill up my dash! :)
